    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">These embeddings are concatenated with the metadata embedding (like the total number of wires) and feed into a NN. The output is a learned latent representation and serves as input to the policy and value networks in Reinforcement Learning. The policy network produces a probability distribution over all possible cell placement for the current node. Then, we can randomly sample the actions based on this probability distribution.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
